k\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gst1665702684426.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gst1665702684426.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gst1665702684426.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gst1665702684426\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $error\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"gst1665702684426___error_262078\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns the Uniface message number for the error.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gst1665702684426__topic_d82613e1_d82614e1_d82615e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gst1665702684426__p_d82616e1_d82617e1_d82618e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$error</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gst1665702684426__topic_d54522e1_d54523e1_d54524e1_d54525e1_d54526e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d736627e66\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gst1665702684426__p_d82622e1_d82623e1_d82624e1\">Uniface message number for the current field or entity data input error.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gst1665702684426__topic_d54527e1_d54528e1_d54529e1_d54530e1_d54531e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d736627e75\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gst1665702684426__p_d82628e1_d82629e1_d82630e1\">Allowed only in error trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gst1665702684426__p_d82631e1_d82632e1_d82633e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gst1665702684426__section_rzn_1ky_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d736627e87\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$error</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">Depending on the error code, you may choose to implement functionality\n               besides just providing a meaningful error message.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example, in the following code a form that lists all the valid\n               codes is displayed if the user enters a code that is not allowed:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"gst1665702684426__pre_fry_1ky_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger error\nvariables\n vSelectedCode\nendvariables\nif ($error = 0126)\n message \"Incorrect code. Select one from list.\"\n activate \"CODES\".exec(vSelectedCode) ; start other form\n if ($status = 1) ; user selected a code\n TYPECD = vSelectedCode ; copy selected value \n return (0) ; allow the user to continue\n else\n message \"No code selected.\"\n return (-1) ; still wrong, so prevent leaving\n endif\nelse\n message $text(\"%%$error\") ;catch all other errors\n return (-1)\nendif\nend; trigger</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hms1665702684501.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$dberror</a><p>Return the error code reported by the DBMS.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jnc1665702576977.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$entname</a><p>Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mgc1665702684351.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger error</a><p>System trigger that is activated when a predefined errors occurs.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528012\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528012\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$error Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $error Returns the Uniface message number for the error. $error Return Values Uniface message number for the current field or entity data input error. Use Allowed only in error trigger. Allowed in all component types. Example: Using $error Depending on the error code, you may choose to implement functionality besides just providing a meaningful error message. For example, in the following code a form that lists all the valid codes is displayed if the user enters a code that is not allowed: trigger error variables vSelectedCode endvariables if ($error = 0126) message \"Incorrect code. Select one from list.\" activate \"CODES\".exec(vSelectedCode) ; start other form if ($status = 1) ; user selected a code TYPECD = vSelectedCode ; copy selected value return (0) ; allow the user to continue else message \"No code selected.\" return (-1) ; still wrong, so prevent leaving endif else message $text(\"%%$error\") ;catch all other errors return (-1) endif end; trigger Copy Related Links $dberror Return the error code reported by the DBMS. $entname Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component. trigger error System trigger that is activated when a predefined errors occurs. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}